summary.para: PivotTable Field Item.
This class is available in Office 2007 and above.
When the object is serialized out as xml, it's qualified name is x:item.

remarks.format:
## Remarks [!INCLUDE[openxmlnoticeiso](~/includes/openxmlnoticeiso.md)]
**item (PivotTable Field Item)**
Represents a single item in PivotTable field.
*[Example:*
```xml <sh:item x="66"/> ```
*end example*]
|Parent Elements| |---------------------| |items (§18.10.1.46)|
[*Note*: The W3C XML Schema definition of this element’s content model (CT_Item) is located in §A.2. *end note*]
[!INCLUDE[openxmlnoticeiso](~/includes/openxmlcopyrightiso.md)]
